data.description: Welcome home in the heart of Poinciana! This spacious 4-bedroom, 2-bathroom residence is a perfect blend of comfort, style, and eco-friendly features. Home includes. Interior Features: Spacious Split Floor Plan. This home offers a thoughtfully designed split floor plan, providing privacy and functionality for families or those who love to entertain. The heart of the home boasts a large kitchen with a stunning center island, perfect for culinary enthusiasts and social gatherings. Modern stainless steel appliances, washer, and dryer are included.   Bright and Airy Living Spaces. Enjoy the abundance of natural light that fills the living spaces, creating a warm and inviting atmosphere.  Eco-Friendly Upgrades: Solar Panels. Experience energy efficiency and cost savings with the installed solar panels, a forward-thinking feature that aligns with a sustainable lifestyle. Exterior Highlights: Fenced-In Backyard. Step into your private oasis with a fenced-in backyard, providing a secure space for your family and pets. The property includes a convenient shed, offering additional storage for tools, equipment, or recreational items. Mature Lawns. The front and backyards feature meticulously maintained mature lawns, enhancing the overall curb appeal and providing a lush backdrop for outdoor activities. Entertain friends and family on the patio area, perfect for summer barbecues, al fresco dining, or simply enjoying the Florida sunshine. Situated in the community of Poinciana, this home offers proximity to local amenities, parks, schools, and shopping centers, ensuring a convenient and enjoyable lifestyle.
